Musuqmaasuqu waa ku takri falka awooda lagu aaminay dano gaar ah. Waxay dhaawacaysaa qof kasta oo noloshiisu, hab-nololeedkiisa ama farxaddiisu ay ku xidhan tahay daacadnimada dadka mansabyada haya.

Waddammada badankood, musuqmaasuqu waa dhib weyn. Masʼuuliinta kharriban badanaa lacagta dadweynaha bay xaddaan. [[Ilaahay]] wuu neceb yahay masuqmaasuqu. Musuqmaasuqa wuu dhamaanayaa. Illahay wuxuu dhawaan qaadi doonaa tallaabo uu dhulkeena uga saarayo musuqmaasuqa.<ref>[https://www.jw.org/en/library/magazines/wp20121001/corruption-will-end/ Corruption Will End!]</ref>.

